<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She loves to dress to the nines for her stint at Heart FM. </p>

<p>And Kelly Brook was channelling sexy office chic when she arrived at the Global Radio HQ in London on Wednesday. </p>

<p>The 40-year-old presenter teamed a silk cream blouse with brown leather cropped trousers which showed off her slim legs. </p>

<p>Working it: Kelly Brook looked chic as she teamed brown leather trousers with nude killer heels as she headed to work at Heart radio in London on Wednesday </p>

<p>Adding some height to her ensemble, she wore a sky high pair of nude Christian Louboutin Pigalle shoes, flashing the brand's iconic red soles. </p>

